<HEAD>Fans Gather, Technicians Scurry As Oscar Night Arrives</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: SUBS 8th graf, `The first ...' to CORRECT `passed' to `past'</NOTE>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto LA2</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By RICHARD DE ATLEY</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associate Press Writer</BYLINE>
