. `` You know full well that virtually all Palestinians regard the <ORGANIZATION> PLO </ORGANIZATION> as their sole legitimate representative,'' he said. `` Your attempts to distinguish the <ORGANIZATION> PLO </ORGANIZATION> from the Palestinian people will not improve your position with Jewish voters in <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> York </LOCATION>, but will, sadly, raise questions among your traditional supporters as to your willingess to stand firm on principle.''
